name: supreme-apparel
description: - Start by adding your info in `_config.yml` - Add as many address lines as you want. Your address will also be used to show your location on the map. - For the emdeded map to work you'll need to [get a key from Google Maps Embed API](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/embed/?hl=en) - In `_layouts/front.html` reorder or remove section as you prefer.
